org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.parquet.vector

Class ParquetDataColumnReaderFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.parquet.vector.ParquetDataColumnReaderFactory

  • public final class ParquetDataColumnReaderFactory
extends Object
    Parquet file has self-describing schema which may differ from the user required schema (e.g. schema evolution). This factory is used to retrieve user required typed data via corresponding reader which reads the underlying data.
